          <p>Low and high fuel price projections come from the HMT Green Book supplementary guidance.<authorialNote marker="28"><p> BEIS (2023), Green Book supplementary guidance, <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/valuation-of-energy-use-and-greenhouse-gas-emissions-for-appraisal"><u>https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/valuation-of-energy-use-and-greenhouse-gas-emissions-for-appraisal</u></a> </p></authorialNote></p>
